WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Rahul: Sounds good. We agreed the current draft is close, but not final yet.

00:00:08.500 --> 00:00:16.500
Maya: I think we should compare the two onboarding variants before making a decision.

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:25.500
Rahul: Maya, you will prepare the comparison deck by Wednesday.

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:35.000
